  • Classes in org.pikater.web.vaadin.gui.server.components.wizards used by org.pikater.web.vaadin.gui.server.components.dbviews.base.expandableview 
    Class and Description
    IWizardCommon
    Interface common for all "state" objects of our own wizards.
    WizardWithDynamicSteps
    Unlike WizardWithOutput which requires statically defined steps, this one allows for each step to construct the next step dynamically.
    WizardWithOutput
    Our own version of a wizard taken from the Wizards Vaadin add-on, that uses a global "state" object (and is thus capable of producing an "output") and is capable of refreshing the newly activated steps, if set to do so (steps may then be a result of previous steps, for example).
